Chivita Active says it has unveiled new 125ml ane 50ml pack sizes for its popular sub-brand, Chivita Active Zest. According to the company, the developments are a strategic move to ensure more product affordability and accessibility to a wider spectrum of Nigerian consumers. The Marketing Director, CHI Limited, Toyin Nnodi, said the new Chivita Active Zest packs are convenient, easy to use, affordable, and will attract more consumers. “We are pleased to launch Chivita Active Zest 125ml and 50ml packs at a very affordable price point enabling more consumers to try as well as enjoy their favourite juice. These forward-looking packs and pocket-friendly pricing represent an important milestone along our journey to make Chivita Active Zest more affordable and accessible to all consumers,” she said.